comment: Kanter (OKC) sets the screen on Snell (CHI) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Mirotic (CHI) makes incidental contact with Roberson (OKC) that does not affect his layup attempt.
LATR shows Snell (CHI) makes contact with Westbrook's (OKC) arm on the drive to the basket.
L-Slash shows Westbrook (OKC) cleanly strips the pass intended for Mirotic (CHI).
Waiters (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly strips the ball from Moore (CHI) on the drive to the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Waiters (OKC) was overturned and OKC was awarded possession.
Kanter (OKC) sets the screen on Moore (CHI) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
RATR shows Roberson (OKC) continues along the path of Brooks (CHI) as he drives to the basket and Brooks initiates contact near the end of the drive.
R-Slash shows Gasol (CHI) dislodges Kanter (OKC) from behind during the rebound attempt.

L-Slash shows Augustin (OKC) has his arms extended toward Mirotic (CHI) when contact is made with Mirotic, who has begun his upward shooting motion. Even though Mirotic initiates the contact, Augustin is in an illegal guarding position and he is assessed
Moore (CHI) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC).
Westbrook (OKC) breaks the plane of the FT line before the ball touches the rim.
Moore (CHI) makes contact with Westbrook's (OKC) arm, dislodging him while he is in the air.
